________________________________________

2. Objectives
•	Conceptual Mastery: To analyze the core features, design philosophy, and diverse industry applications of Python.
•	Environment Configuration: To successfully deploy the Anaconda Distribution and initialize the Jupyter Notebook environment on a local machine.
•	IDE Exploration: To evaluate the strengths and weaknesses of different development environments (Local vs. Cloud-based).
